Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:13.93,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞  玩偶装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说绫音那里也被偷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在橱柜里的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷跑进神社里会遭天遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上会出现小偷  真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近谷类和蔬菜  好像都被偷了好几棵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点不安心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  究竟是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  今天还真早…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸上有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是熊熊的蜜罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吃的  承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就承认了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  虽然饭团  水果  蜂蜜  馒头是我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他可不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道认为偷全村食物的小偷会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的平时的行为太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连行人大人都这样看待我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失落成这样  就是说真的不是麻知姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行踪不明的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  行人大人一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在违抗姐姐大人的话会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能放任小偷不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  我们也帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在三天前被偷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那被偷什么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  没看到过这么拼命的麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么麻烦的事情谁去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去的…乐意至极…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来被偷的很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件从村子最北边开始慢慢延伸到南边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后昨晚是海龙神社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  小偷盯上的下个地方会是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这条线最近的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概会是香里家或者是雪乃家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  那么今晚只要去监视的话也许就能抓住犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为分两组的抽签  不准互相抱怨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会又使诈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你先抽不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你干杯  发光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公子一起在夕阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直玩到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜小铃的机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去香里家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:07:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之晚上不得不聚在一起守小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷会是怎么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上以前都没有过这种坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是小偷干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些全部都吃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明每天都只偷一家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天却是海龙神社和黄瓜地两家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往推想的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人还没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家的时候常常开夜车的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐气势十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被诬陷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睁着眼睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…就不会困了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此…彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  猫头鹰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然接住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么黑的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就揭穿你的真实面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头部脱出了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被砍下的人头?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…被拽下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个头套
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  为什么是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守的话我一个人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先睡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人来  小铃就待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  小偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你认识的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篓筐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  为什么要钻进篓筐里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长在别人面前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一家都在演杂技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我从以前开始就很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上一直失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了克服害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了独自的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是和以前一样无法和人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避人眼目在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能好好地交到朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样的我在途中也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人开始一起旅行不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱用光了想坐船回国的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被暴风雨卷入…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来的时候就发现漂流到这个岛上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 也不用一一画在纸上说明…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然每天都下决心…今天要出现在大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又太害羞又犹豫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这样就事件解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过偷东西可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…想让你们分我点东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却开不了口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…对不起了…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  黄瓜地的是不是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  把田地全都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不知道…那不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的人果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是说我也很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄瓜地也许是你的朋友做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野先生非常喜欢黄瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那朋友也漂流到了这个岛上太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知被嫁祸了不是很生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道梅梅是犯人  不知道会做出什么事情来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先回家  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音把这个给我 说是犯人似乎戴着这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸糊的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅连这个都戴着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在追踪这个气味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到也是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是千影家的黄瓜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这个程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道黄瓜小偷是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气味和刚才面具的是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  气味消失了 难道是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这种地方徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗  被抓住就很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  在我回这里之前要老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野先生…远野先生是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…都两人一起旅行着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到远野先生就在附近  就坐立不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快点见到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…行人先生  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  犬犬好像知道远野先生在哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气味消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳过去的话有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没有可以藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法骗过我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐…听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我找的多幸苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你不要乱跑乱动了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河童吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫远野先生一直以为是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童什么虚构动物根本不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然嫁祸给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然向我挑衅  真有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…请等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷食物的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野先生没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真正的犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起…饶恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对做坏事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给予惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也好好道歉了 就饶恕她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道理由  看起来不像是坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人误会是大姐头平时的行为不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经那么道歉了  还惩罚的话那是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉我才是坏人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然行人大人这样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得平复下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此岛上增加了新的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:03.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅和远野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是非常奇怪的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上的却人也非常的和蔼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许很快就会令人意外地融洽相处了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…活该…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好
